Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要砍掉…『七鄉』！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是元老院的一致意見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』的開花給世界帶來了多大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在危機已經變成現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不可固守不出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 這個城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著『七鄉』的毀滅而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一個城鎮的代價便可以拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個…城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個城鎮毀滅了 妖怪們會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從円神出現開始 妳以為過了多長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間沒有做出成果的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的撤離就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作為町長最後的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:47.32,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(475,325)}荊棘之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前花剛剛開 這次又是這種奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會又是你們做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 町長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是明擺著的嗎 沒關…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關…系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 元老院準備想要切斷『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌亂的衝進去又會被土地神幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界已經被破壞的現在 不是還有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說過了的 其他的妖怪優先治療
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 『調率』是非常危險的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍錯一點 秋名會和送歸的妖怪一起到那個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就好 今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被『調率』的妖怪會非常痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 『調率』是修正人界和妖界的次元偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妖怪更加方便進入那邊的世界而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比被滅殺要輕鬆很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為那就如字面意思是殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華 妳沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 樹裡幫我戴上的新枷似乎很奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡邏中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不會猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長好長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很長 但是很暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要安靜一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 已經可以說話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕…留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上這個就看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍微有點長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 所以才說的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿給我 幫妳修短
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身行李是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正準備去避難…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好在城外有棲身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避難？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從生活相談事務所的人那聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「為了以防萬一 請準備好」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 空地或者體育館都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 對不起 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託過了 但是果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 說到收容妖怪 什麼地方的城鎮都會討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會有這城鎮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒時間消沉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可去的居民還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得下了避難的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是存在可能性 為了萬一的時候做準備而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是町長不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長怎麼能不優先考慮居民的安全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只是為了萬一 秋名也這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼 抱歉 樹裡那裡人手不夠 去幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄城鎮而逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說這種事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從元老院的擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把居民從城鎮撤離出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元老院會立刻砍掉『七鄉』的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要為了不砍掉而留下居民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在這樣做會給居民帶來多餘的不安而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上存在危險的可能 怎麼會是無用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要逃避而已不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從円神身邊逃避不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道城鎮安全了 就馬上會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神嗎 已經刻不容緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始切斷『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回小姐那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『八彩』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在騷亂之中已經被對方得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從外部送入妖力 已經完全把『七鄉』吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方動了腦筋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力這東西的話 將其增輻也能從遠處進行傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和電波一個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨她去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬她一個人沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這點程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『火焰噴射器』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物由我們來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 把姬帶到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？故障？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用…我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『圍』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終段『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…由我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快送到樹裡小姐那去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還說再開心一會的 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下已成定局了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神不是無法離開自己負責的土地的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然從那麼遠的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳已經放棄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是龍的化身 傷勢並沒有那麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過所積累疲勞也並不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站到現在也只能用不可思議來形容了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她一直都在練功…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 生命倒無危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時休息下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來後一定是這種表情就跑外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別阻止她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我必須去看看其他患者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部自己來背負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元老院沒察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力將力量限制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要砍也砍不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 城鎮裡離『七鄉』最遠的地方是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心部 元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 請到元老院避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是管理城鎮的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間說明了 這裡很危險 大家快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是櫻真町『七鄉』即將開花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即去元老院避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請避難 『七鄉』的開花是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華妳不用來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是全部人員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面還有一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要叫她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去找姬定會碰釘子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹裡小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定在等你哦 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒忘過這天花板了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從這傷之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實什麼都沒改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣也是想努力下的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡全力練習 公務 巡邏 都是一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍槍也用不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有什麼情況 也都是讓秋名你們出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為町長 為人所愛 為城鎮所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍所愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為町長 作為町長卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀的事 我也不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡銀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我必須要保護城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為町長本不應該說這些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最差勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡給大家帶來痛苦 自己卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該如何是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起保護城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥說過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與秋名 與姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來保護城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不靜養是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼艱巨的任務 不會那麼快就結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 但現在就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要姬的力量的時候一定會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 能幫我按摩下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 客人身體好僵哦 凝固的8 BEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當神也有很多煩心事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好想瞭解下神仙大人哦 講來聽聽吧 講來聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 下回是我的「不准出手事」的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 煩躁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著按下腰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.71,0:24:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神也會積累呢 贅肉
